data.description: Attention car lovers! Newly remodeled 3 bed/2 bath home on huge corner lot. Great opportunity to have a body shop in your back yard! Huge detached garage with parking for multiple cars + fully functioning PAINT BAY! The home was just freshly painted throughout and features brand new appliances in kitchen and metal roof. Large primary bedroom with en suite bath and large walk-in closet. The walk-in closet could easily be converted into a 4th bedroom if needed. Third room is a flex room which could be a large 3rd bedroom, game room, movie room or home office. Lots of potential for the right buyer to have a home and business all in one. Assumable & affordable flood insurance policy is in place!
